#: etesyncresource.cpp:206
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Your EteSync credentials were changed. Please click OK to re-enter your "
"credentials."
msgstr ""
"Poverilnice za EteSync so bile spremenjene. Kliknite V redu, če želite znova "
"vnesti svoje poverilnice."

